{"tid":1530571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"喇沙外有防暴警搜查校友　另一校生稱戴黑口罩或記大過.    嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院拒絕學生入內並沒收物資","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:03:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32266661d51296a2f32ef9ced83738f2384026e2","tid":1530571,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478330-20190902.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478330-20190902.htm&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=3f772071\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478330-20190902.htm&h=285ab3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478330-20190902.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有多間學校的學生趁開學日參與罷課。其中在喇沙書院，有學生在上課前默站，有校友自發在校門外派傳單，呼籲同學參與罷課。<br />\n<br />\n在早上約10時，有防暴警察到喇沙書院外，搜查校友的隨身物品，了解校友聚集的目的。據了解，警方指有市民看到有人聚集可能有擔憂，強調只要和平理性、沒有違例便沒有問題，其後警員離去。喇沙書院回應查詢時表示，沒有報警。<br />\n<br />\n另外，嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院反修例關注組在社交平台上表示，校方拒絕讓攜帶物資的學生進入校園，並無理沒收部分物資，要求戴上黑色口罩的學生換上普通口罩，並引述有老師指，若學生不除下黑口罩，會被記大過。"},{"pid":"bbc88ee6e681d155a8e7ecd87a7e31629e9e1b8b","tid":1530571,"uid":61417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"屌，幫手推下有用post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要報平安，我要搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［人手置頂］被捕需知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6fc1d12615942acf40fb21eb294294a1be812f2","tid":1530571,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94615d831c8c78301a6eeb60a0633f3ed94bcd4e","tid":1530571,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a49368d4c188a61b2f6f44454961480370f891d","tid":1530571,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:03:49.000Z","msg":"如果李家超自殺<br />\n大家想條畜生撚樣點樣死法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}